            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288217</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 推出全新 Galaxy S25 系列旗艦手機，包括 Galaxy S25、S25+ 和 S25 Ultra。設計上 S25 Ultra、S25 和 S25+ 都採用了更圓潤的邊角設計，提升手感之餘，也讓整個系列更具統一感。S25 Ultra 的邊框則以鈦金屬製造，持機時有更高級感覺，其餘型號使用鋁金屬邊框。屏幕尺寸方面，S25、S25+ 和 S25 Ultra 分別為 6.2 吋、6.7 吋和 6.9 吋，其中 Ultra 型號熒幕邊框更窄，令單手操作更加方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288314" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288322" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxys25ultrafeatur-694x355.png" alt="" width="694" height="355" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxys25ultrafeatur-694x355.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxys25ultrafeatur.png 1094w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>設計改進</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>更圓角設計</strong>：S25 Ultra、S25 和 S25+ 的設計更為統一，改用較圓角的機身，手感提升，握持更舒適。</li><li><strong>輕薄機身</strong>：熒幕增大 0.1 吋但保持與上代相似的機身尺寸，邊框更窄，單手操控無壓力。</li><li><strong>玻璃材質</strong>：採用更耐用的 Corning Gorilla Glass Victus 2。</li><li><strong>機身顏色</strong>：4 種鈦金屬色選擇：黑、灰、藍、銀。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25 Ultra 熒幕尺寸為 6.9 吋</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288370" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-12-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-12-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-12.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25+ 以大熒幕為賣點，其熒幕尺寸為 6.7 吋，而想要握感更實在的朋友可考慮 Galaxy S25 其熒幕尺寸為 6.2 吋</p><p style="text-align: center;"><h2>Galaxy S25 Ultra 設計特色</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08518-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08518-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08518.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Galaxy S25 Ultra 設有鈦金屬黑、鈦金屬灰、鈦金屬藍及鈦金屬銀 4 種機身顏色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288360" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288359" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另 Samsung 官方網站有提供另外三款鈦金屬綠色、Jetblack 以及粉金色</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288373" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-15-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-15-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-15.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288374" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-16-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-16-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-16.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-17-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-17-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-17.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25 Ultra 設計是更為纖薄、圓潤的邊角，令手握感覺更好</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-18-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-18-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-18.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288377" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-19-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-19-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/unboxinggalaxys25ser-19.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25 Ultra 備有內置 S-Pen 輕觸筆可從機身取出</p><br /><b><ul><li><strong>表格保存與分享</strong>：生成的表格可儲存為圖檔，直接用於 Instagram 或其他社交平台的圖文併茂貼文。</li></ul></li><li><strong>轉置功能</strong>：用户可靈活切換表格 X/Y 軸，適應不同數據分析需求。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288316" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-4.jpg 1920w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-16-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-16-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/galaxyunpackedjanuar-16.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Samsung Galaxy S25 Ultra 延續了 Ultra 系列的高規格硬件，同時專注於 Galaxy AI 功能的實用性升級，讓日常操作更方便。設計更為輕薄與令操作更舒適，適合追求效能與便利的用家。</p><h2>預計發售日期與價格</h2><p>Galaxy S25 Ultra 與 S25 系列其他機款預定於 2 月 7 日上市，除了旗艦級的 S25 Ultra 起售價為 1,299 美元（約港幣 HK$10,132），S25 Plus 和標準版 S25 的定價分別為 1,000 美元（約港幣 HK$7,800）與 800 美元（約港幣 HK$6,240）。</p><p>在 Samsung 發佈香港售價後，我們也會更新上列售價。</p><h2><strong>基本規格</strong></h2><ul><li><h3>Galaxy S25 Ultra</h3><ul><li><strong>顯示屏</strong>：6.9 吋 QHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X，120Hz 更新率 (1~120Hz)，Vision Booster，Adaptive Color Tone</li><li><strong>尺寸與重量</strong>：77.6 x 162.8 x 8.2 mm，218g</li><li><strong>相機</strong>：
<ul><li>50MP 超廣角：F1.9, FOV 120˚</li><li>200MP 廣角：OIS F1.7, FOV 85˚</li><li>50MP 長焦：5x 光學變焦, OIS F3.4, FOV 22˚</li><li>10MP 長焦：3x 光學變焦, OIS F2.4, FOV 36˚</li><li>12MP 前置：F2.2, FOV 80˚</li></ul></li><li><strong>記憶體與儲存空間</strong>：12GB + 1TB / 12GB + 512GB / 12GB + 256GB</li><li><strong>電池</strong>：5,000 mAh，支援 45W 有線快充與無線充電</li><li><strong>作業系統</strong>：Android 15, One UI 7</li><li><strong>網路與連線</strong>：5G, LTE, Wi-Fi 7, Bluetooth 5.4</li><li><strong>防水防塵</strong>：IP68</li></ul><hr /><h3>Galaxy S25</h3><ul><li><strong>顯示屏</strong>：6.2 吋 FHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X，120Hz 更新率 (1~120Hz)，Vision Booster，Adaptive Color Tone</li><li><strong>尺寸與重量</strong>：70.5 x 146.9 x 7.2 mm，162g</li><li><strong>相機</strong>：
