            <title>Tesla 洛杉磯餐飲充電複合站將竣工，應用程式代碼透露可用 App 點餐</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/tesla-la-diner-opening/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-la-diner-opening</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/22/tesla-la-diner-opening/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 13:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288280</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Tesla 在 2022 年已申請在洛杉磯興建一個結合餐飲娛樂的超級充電站的綜合項目，期望為 Tesla 車主提供便利與舒適的全新體驗。最近該超級充電站綜合項目竣工在即，有人在附近實拍了現場圖片，另外亦有媒體在 Tesla 應用程式發現更多細節，可以預計充電站會提供餐飲娛樂服務。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">What’s round and shiny but still not yet open?<br />
Tesla diner</p><p>Lots of Supercharging stalls being installed in the adjacent lot <a href="https://t.co/Ggl5iZE205">pic.twitter.com/Ggl5iZE205</a></p><p>— AL Set (@AlSet51241438) <a href="https://twitter.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 4, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288283" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha.jpg 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AL Set 分享的 Tesla 餐廳充電站圖片，圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501">AlSet51241438@X</a></p><p>Tesla 在應用程式中新增餐廳服務功能，車主能通過手機選擇餐飲服務。據《Wuangus》報道，iOS 版本最新 Tesla 應用程式代碼新增了部分與餐飲有關之詞彙，例如「show_diner」、「Diner Home Screen」、「profile_settings_diner_description」和「View menu &amp; amenities」，顯示車主未來可透過 Tesla 應用程式查看是日餐牌，甚至可以直接從 Tesla App 點餐。由於 Tesla 知悉車主使用哪個超級充電站，因此可以預期 Tesla 餐飲充電複合站將會提供送餐服務，無須車主自行取餐。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288282" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/00_tesla_compound_re-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/00_tesla_compound_re-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/00_tesla_compound_re.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲2023 年 Tesla 展示的設計圖，圖片來源：<a href="https://wuangus.cc/tesla-los-angeles-restaurant-opening-soon/">Wu Angus</a></p><p>據 AL Set 分享的圖片影片顯示，餐廳已將近竣工，但目前 Tesla 仍未公佈正式啟用日期。外界期待這家餐廳成為洛杉磯電動車生態圈的新地標，推動充電設施的多元化發展，讓車主在充電期間，既能享受豐富餐飲，亦可放鬆片刻。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288284" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/teslaladinersupercha-1.jpg 2048w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲AL Set 分享的 Tesla 餐廳充電站圖片，圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501">AlSet51241438@X</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://electrek.co/2025/01/21/tesla-points-to-diner-integration-in-app-insurance-discount-with-full-self-driving-and-more/">Electrek</a>、<a href="https://www.teslarati.com/teslas-la-diner-and-charger-gets-closer-but-when-will-it-be-done/">Teslarati</a>、<a href="https://x.com/AlSet51241438/status/1875656107223609501">AlSet51241438@X</a>、<a href="https://wuangus.cc/tesla-los-angeles-restaurant-opening-soon/">Wu Angus</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
